# REST Client Environment Configuration
# Select environment in VS Code bottom bar: "development" or "production"
# Install REST Client extension: https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=humao.rest-client

### Login - Get JWT token (sets httpOnly cookie)
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### Logout - Clear JWT token
POST {{host}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

### Get current user info (requires authentication)
GET {{host}}/api/auth/me
Content-Type: application/json

